            <title>[GROOVY-4438] Use of an inner enum causes compilation to go into infinite loop</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4438</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following piece of code causes the compilation to go into infinite loop&lt;/p&gt;

